The paper deals with salient object detection using hyperspectral images, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. The dataset creation and evaluation involve image processing (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) methods. The use of spectral features in hyperspectral images also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques.
